<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="25Jan1938"><font color="red">25 January 1938</font> <i>NLCV</i> (from Viscount Carlow to Paul L&eacute;on): Thank you for your letter of 22nd January &hellip; the books are being held up by the binders, who have had some difficulty with the colour of the vellum skins. </div>
